ProcedureHelp.#cdata:
Syntax: PROC PRODUCT_STATUS; 
  RUN;

PROC PRODUCT_STATUS returns a list of the SAS Foundation products that are installed on your system, 
along with the version numbers of those products. It provides a quick method to determine whether a 
SAS product is available for your use. The results from PROC PRODUCT_STATUS are returned to the SAS 
log.
